						<summary>

						<p>Pillar in the <hi rend="italic">mukha-maṇḍapa</hi> of the Talakaṇṭamma shrine.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Krōdhana, Māgha śu. 8, Tuesday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. It seems to register the apportionment of the <hi rend="italic">vṛittis</hi> of the temple land between the two sons of a certain jīya. In characters of 16th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>[<hi rend="italic">Ibid.,</hi> No. 292] half portion.</p>						

						</summary>
